timelineItems.name: Edward
timelineItems.text: #NERevs we don't need Barbasol in New England we don't shave our beards! Go Revs!

timelineItems.name: NE Revolution
timelineItems.text: We're underway from MAPFRE Stadium, where the #NERevs are closing out a two-game road trip against #CrewSC. #CLBvNE http://t.co/vU969xCjCs

timelineItems.name: Brian O'Connell
timelineItems.text: I'd be worried if the #NERevs had defensive depth issues. Oh wait, nevermind. #CLBvNE

timelineItems.name: John
timelineItems.text: Agudelo and Bunbury should switch. #NERevs

timelineItems.name: Chris Goodwin
timelineItems.text: So Heaps is playing Bunbury in a spot he's not comfortable to.....why again? #BadCoaching #NERevs

timelineItems.name: Carlos D. Mojica
timelineItems.text: #NERevs trying to force #CrewSC to make more mistakes in midfield. #CLBvNE

timelineItems.name: Matt LaPan
timelineItems.text: Well Ive been calling Lee Nguyen out recently. A 1st minute goal cures some evils. Maybe another one to make me feel good? #NERevs

timelineItems.name: Patrick Murphy
timelineItems.text: When Tchani gets the ball #NERevs are putting numbers around him. At least two on both of his touches in the offensive half. #CrewSC

timelineItems.name: JT Chang
timelineItems.text: Giving up the equalizer so quickly sucks, but Nguyen put a shot on goal. Maybe his 30% shot accuracy will start to climb #NERevs

timelineItems.name: El CapitÃ¡n AbrÃ¡m
timelineItems.text: Weird that no #NERevs is going to the Gold Cup? I thought for sure we'd lose Agudelo. I'm not exactly mad, but was sure we'd lose somebody.

timelineItems.name: Greg Benson
timelineItems.text: Mazy run by Higuain leads to a shot that Shuttleworth has to do well to save. Kamara can't put away rebound from a tough angle. #CLBvNE

timelineItems.name: Matt LaPan
timelineItems.text: Revs defense has to wake up. Shocked Kamara missed the net there. Leading scorer in MLS. Gotta mark him #NERevs

timelineItems.name: birdboy2000
timelineItems.text: We miss AJ Soares. #NERevs

timelineItems.name: Matt LaPan
timelineItems.text: Daigo is battling right now. Making Heaps look smart for starting him #NERevs

timelineItems.name: Daniel Karell
timelineItems.text: One thing I’ve noticed so far is that #CrewSC is doing a really good job pulling the #NERevs midfield and defenders forward and backwards

timelineItems.name: Joe Tansey
timelineItems.text: Higuain's feeling it tonight. Very positive start for #CrewSC minus the early concession. #CLBvNE

timelineItems.name: Daniel Karell
timelineItems.text: #NERevs at this point are all behind the ball and are just firing the ball clear instead of keeping possession.

timelineItems.text: This is the first game in a long time where as a #NERevs fan I’ve had the feeling that the opponent seems to have more players on the field.
